                Refinancing
              </h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-800">
                <li>✓ Replace existing loan with new one</li>
                <li>✓ Typically get better terms/rates</li>
                <li>✓ Access equity as cash</li>
                <li>✓ Requires good payment history</li>
                <li>✓ New financier pays off old loan</li>
